It  brings me a Great Joy to Inform you All that I have won a Bronze medal🏅 in the National Masters Classic Powerlifting Championship 2023🏋️‍♀️🏋️‍♀️ Held at Rajam , Andhra Pradesh 12 to16July.
 After a Tragic Accident 11 months ago where my Right Hand Humerus Bone was fractured, and Undergone  a very Serious Surgery. 🏥Post-surgery a Titanium Plate with  12 Screws was attached to my Hand and people told me that I could never lift again. 
 The Strong Desire and Passion towards the Game Self Motivated me to GET BACK into Lifting Weights again. 🏋️‍♀️🏋️‍♀️
 It has been a Wonderful Journey to Receive this Accolade at this moment and I sincerely Thank All of you for the  Seamless Support in my Powerlifting Journey so far.
